{"url": "https://www.ics.uci.edu/~kobsa/courses/ICS104/course-notes/input-devices.htm", "content": "<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC \"-//w3c//dtd html 4.0 transitional//en\">\n<html><head>\n\n\n\n\n   <meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=iso-8859-1\">\n   <meta name=\"GENERATOR\" content=\"Mozilla/4.72 (Macintosh; I; PPC) [Netscape]\"><title>Input devices</title></head><body bgcolor=\"#ffffff\">\n&nbsp; <big><font face=\"Arial,Helvetica\"><font size=\"6\"><big>Input devices</big></font></font></big> \n<ul><big> </big><li><big> <font face=\"Arial,Helvetica\" size=\"+2\"><big>Keyboards<font face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\"><a href=\"keyboards.jpg\"><i><img src=\"../../../Graphics%20Templates/Diamonds/Di-red.gif\" alt=\"The linked image shows several keyboard layouts: regular typewriter keyboard, function keys added at the left or the top line, numeric keypad added at the right side.\" border=\"0\" height=\"11\" width=\"11\"></i></a></font> \n(QWERTY</big></font><font size=\"+2\"><big><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Querty\"><img style=\"border: 0px solid ; width: 14px; height: 14px;\" alt=\"Link to Wikipedia entry on the QUERTY keyboard\" src=\"../../../graphics/192px-Icon_External_Link.svg.png\"></a></big></font><font face=\"Arial,Helvetica\" size=\"+2\"><big>, Dvorak<font face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\"><a href=\"dvorak-layout.gif\"><i><img src=\"../../../Graphics%20Templates/Diamonds/Di-red.gif\" alt=\"The linked image shows the layout of a Dvorak keyboard.\" border=\"0\" height=\"11\" width=\"11\"></i></a></font></big></font><font size=\"+2\"><big><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dvorak_Simplified_Keyboard\"><img style=\"border: 0px solid ; width: 14px; height: 14px;\" alt=\"Link to Wikipedia entry on Dvorak keyboard\" src=\"../../../graphics/192px-Icon_External_Link.svg.png\"></a></big></font><font face=\"Arial,Helvetica\" size=\"+2\"><big>,\n\nchord<a href=\"keyboard_twiddler.jpg\"><font face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\"><i><img style=\"border: 0px solid ; width: 11px; height: 11px;\" src=\"../../../Graphics%20Templates/Diamonds/Di-red.gif\" alt=\"The linked image shows the &quot;twiddler&quot;, a chord keyboard developed at MIT. It only has a dozen of keys and is operated by pressing several keys at the same time.\"></i></font></a>,\n\nnumeric)</big></font></big></li><big>\n  </big><li><big> <font face=\"Arial,Helvetica\" size=\"+2\"><big>Cursor keys</big></font></big></li><li><big><font face=\"Arial,Helvetica\" size=\"+2\"><big>mouse \n(1-3 buttons)</big></font></big></li>\n  <li><big><font face=\"Arial,Helvetica\" size=\"+2\"><big>trackballs, trackpads, \njoystick, 3D-mouse <font face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\"><a href=\"Head_cube_6button_close.jpg\"><i><img src=\"../../../Graphics%20Templates/Diamonds/Di-red.gif\" alt=\"The linked image shows a device that can be used for rotating three-dimensional virtual reality objects. It has three protuding axes that can be rotated to turn the object around the respective dimension.\" border=\"0\" height=\"11\" width=\"11\"></i></a><i>&nbsp;<a href=\"spaceball3D.gif\"><img style=\"border: 0px solid ; width: 11px; height: 11px;\" src=\"../../../Graphics%20Templates/Diamonds/Di-red.gif\" alt=\"The linked image shows a device that can be used for rotating three-dimensional virtual reality objects. It has three protuding axes that can be rotated to turn the object around the respective dimension.\"></a></i></font></big></font></big></li>\n<li><big> \n    <font face=\"Arial,Helvetica\" size=\"+2\"><big>Touch screens</big></font></big></li></ul><ul><big> </big><li><big> \n    <font face=\"Arial,Helvetica\" size=\"+2\"><big>Speech input</big></font></big></li></ul><ul><big> </big><li><big><font face=\"Arial,Helvetica\" size=\"+2\"><big>\"Graffiti\"</big></font><font face=\"Arial,Helvetica\" size=\"+2\"><big><font face=\"Arial,Helvetica\"><font face=\"Arial,Helvetica\"><font face=\"Arial,Helvetica\"><font face=\"Arial,Helvetica\"><font face=\"Arial,Helvetica\"><font face=\"Arial,Helvetica\"><font face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\"><a href=\"graffitisheet.png\"><i><img src=\"../../../Graphics%20Templates/Diamonds/Di-red.gif\" alt=\"The linked image shows &quot;graffiti&quot; for the Palm pilot, i.e. simplified characters for data entry.\" border=\"0\" height=\"11\" width=\"11\"></i></a></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></big></font><font face=\"Arial,Helvetica\" size=\"+2\"><big>, \nhandwriting, gestures</big></font></big></li><big>\n  </big></ul><ul><big> </big><li><big><font face=\"Arial,Helvetica\" size=\"+2\"><big>Data\n      \ngloves</big></font><font face=\"Arial,Helvetica\" size=\"+2\"><big><font face=\"Arial,Helvetica\"><font face=\"Arial,Helvetica\"><font face=\"Arial,Helvetica\"><font face=\"Arial,Helvetica\"><font face=\"Arial,Helvetica\"><font face=\"Arial,Helvetica\"><font face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\"><a href=\"dataglove.jpg\"><i><img src=\"../../../Graphics%20Templates/Diamonds/Di-red.gif\" alt=\"The linked image shows a so-called &quot;data glove&quot; that has mechanical flexion sensors on the back of the hand so that the position of the fingers can be monitored.\" border=\"0\" height=\"11\" width=\"11\"></i></a></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></big></font><font face=\"Arial,Helvetica\" size=\"+2\"><big> </big></font><font face=\"Arial,Helvetica\" size=\"+2\"><big><font face=\"Arial,Helvetica\"><font face=\"Arial,Helvetica\"><font face=\"Arial,Helvetica\"><font face=\"Arial,Helvetica\"><font face=\"Arial,Helvetica\"><font face=\"Arial,Helvetica\"><font face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\"><a href=\"dataglove2.jpg\"><i><img src=\"../../../Graphics%20Templates/Diamonds/Di-red.gif\" alt=\"The linked image shows a so-called &quot;data glove&quot; that has optical flexion sensors on the back of the hand so that the position of the fingers can be monitored.\" border=\"0\" height=\"11\" width=\"11\"></i></a></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></big></font><font face=\"Arial,Helvetica\" size=\"+2\"><big>,\n\ndata suits<font face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\"><a href=\"datasuit.jpg\"><i><img src=\"../../../Graphics%20Templates/Diamonds/Di-red.gif\" alt=\"The linked image shows a device that can be used for rotating three-dimensional virtual reality objects. It has three protuding axes that can be rotated to turn the object around the respective dimension.\" border=\"0\" height=\"11\" width=\"11\"></i></a></font>,\n3D trackers</big></font></big></li><big>\n  </big></ul>\n<ul><big> </big><li><big><font face=\"Arial,Helvetica\" size=\"+2\"><big>Gaze</big></font></big></li><big>\n  </big></ul>\n<ul><big>\n  </big><li><big><font face=\"Arial,Helvetica\" size=\"+2\"><big>Thought </big></font><font size=\"+2\"><big><a href=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1VPY1d2t_FE\"><img style=\"border: 0px solid ; width: 14px; height: 14px;\" alt=\"Link to YouTube video on thought control of wheelchair\" src=\"../../../graphics/192px-Icon_External_Link.svg.png\"></a></big></font></big></li><big>\n  </big></ul>\n<ul><big> \n  </big><li><big><font face=\"Arial,Helvetica\" size=\"+2\"><big>Special input devices for people with \ndisabilities<br>\n \n    </big></font><font face=\"Arial,Helvetica\" size=\"+2\"><big>(e.g., foot \nmouse, <font face=\"Arial,Helvetica\">head mouse<font face=\"Arial,Helvetica\"><font face=\"Arial,Helvetica\"><font face=\"Arial,Helvetica\"><font face=\"Arial,Helvetica\"><font face=\"Arial,Helvetica\"><font face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\"><a href=\"headmouse.jpg\"><i><img src=\"../../../Graphics%20Templates/Diamonds/Di-red.gif\" alt=\"The linked image shows a tracking device attached to a computer that monitors the movements of a reflector on the user's front and imploys this input for mouse cursor movements.\" border=\"0\" height=\"11\" width=\"11\"></i></a></font></font></font></font></font></font></font> <font face=\"Arial,Helvetica\"><font face=\"Arial,Helvetica\"><font face=\"Arial,Helvetica\"><font face=\"Arial,Helvetica\"><font face=\"Arial,Helvetica\"><font face=\"Arial,Helvetica\"><font face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\"><a href=\"headmouse-suction-tube.jpg\"><i><img src=\"../../../Graphics%20Templates/Diamonds/Di-red.gif\" alt=\"The linked image shows a tracking device attached to a computer that monitors the movements of a reflector on the user's front and imploys this input for mouse cursor movements.\" border=\"0\" height=\"11\" width=\"11\"></i></a></font></font></font></font></font></font></font>, \nlip readers, etc.)</big></font> </big></li><big>\n  </big></ul>\n<p><big><font size=\"+2\"><big><br>\n<span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica;\"><span style=\"font-style: italic;\"><img style=\"width: 62px; height: 40px;\" alt=\"Finger pointing right\" src=\"../../../graphics/pointing-finger-right3.jpg\"></span></span><i><font face=\"Arial,Helvetica\">&nbsp; Cater\n    to variety of input devices</font></i></big></font></big>\n  <font size=\"6\"> </font></p>\n\n</body></html>", "encoding": "ascii"}